data.comment: The match has started.
Throw-in for Urawa in the half of Nagoya.
In the minute 1, Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Nagoya in their own half.
Throw-in for Urawa at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium.
Urawa to take a throw-in in Nagoya territory.
In the minute 3, Urawa have a dangerous throw-in.
Throw-in for Urawa close to the penalty box.
In Nagoya a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 6, Masaaki Iemoto signals a free kick to Nagoya.
Nagoya have been awarded a corner by Masaaki Iemoto.
Goal kick for Urawa at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium.
In the minute 8, In Nagoya, Urawa push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
Goal! Nagoya have got their heads in front thanks to a Naoki Maeda strike.
Goal! Nagoya extend their lead to 2-0 through Naoki Maeda.
In the minute 10, Mateus instrumental with a fine assist.
Throw-in for Urawa in their own half.
Can Urawa capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Nagoya's half?
In the minute 16, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Mateus (Nagoya) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Corner awarded to Nagoya.
In the minute 18, Goal! Joao Schmidt extends Nagoya's lead to 3-0 in Nagoya with a header.
Gabriel Xavier with an assist there.
Ball safe as Urawa is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 20, Free kick for Urawa in the half of Nagoya.
Kai Shibato (Urawa) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Nagoya awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 25, Masaaki Iemoto awards Urawa a goal kick.
Throw-in Nagoya.
Nagoya are in shooting range from this free kick.
In the minute 30, Mateus for Nagoya gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Ball goes out of play for a Urawa goal kick.
Free kick for Nagoya in their own half.
In the minute 30, Koya Yuruki (Urawa) has received a yellow card from Masaaki Iemoto.
Free kick Nagoya.
Nagoya's Mateus gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 32, It's a goal kick for the away team in Nagoya.
Urawa's Leonardo misses with an attempt on goal.
Nagoya have a goal kick.
In the minute 34, Masaaki Iemoto awards the home team a throw-in.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a Urawa throw-in in Nagoya's half.
Goal! Naoki Maeda extends Nagoya's lead to 4-0.
In the minute 38, Great play from Gabriel Xavier to set up the goal.
Nagoya needs to be cautious. Urawa have an attacking throw-in.
Nagoya drive upfield and Gabriel Xavier gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Urawa defender.
In the minute 44, Ryosuke Yamanaka (Urawa) fires in a shot â€“ and hits the post!
In the minute 45, 2 minutes of injury time will be added to the 1st half.
The ref's whistle signals the end of the first-half.
Goal! Nagoya extend their lead to 5-0 through Gabriel Xavier.
That's a fine assist from Mu Kanazaki.
Masaaki Iemoto has blown to start the second-half.
In the minute 46, Mu Kanazaki of Nagoya gets in a strike, but is off target.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Nagoya.
In the minute 46, Tsuyoshi Otsuki (Urawa) is making a third substitution, with Takahiro Sekine replacing Kosuke Taketomi.
The away team have replaced Koya Yuruki with Yuki Muto. This is the second substitution made today by Tsuyoshi Otsuki.
Tomoaki Makino is replacing Daisuke Suzuki for the away team.
Goal! Leonardo pulls one back for Urawa to make it 5-1.
In the minute 49, Leonardo gets his shot on target but fails to score for Urawa.
Nagoya push upfield but Masaaki Iemoto quickly pulls them for offside.
Nagoya take a comfortable 6-1 lead thanks to Naoki Maeda.
In the minute 50, That's a fine assist from Mu Kanazaki.
Yuki Muto (Urawa) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Can Urawa get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Nagoya's half?
In the minute 53, Nagoya make their first substitution with Yuki Soma replacing Naoki Maeda.
The home team replace Joao Schmidt with Yosuke Akiyama.
Ball safe as Nagoya is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 54, Yosuke Akiyama for Nagoya drives towards goal at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Throw-in high up the field for Urawa in Nagoya.
Masaaki Iemoto awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 58, Urawa have a goal kick.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a throw-in for Urawa, close to Nagoya's area.
Free kick for Urawa in the half of Nagoya.
Urawa advance rapidly upfield but Masaaki Iemoto blows for offside.
In the minute 61, Kazuki Nagasawa is on a sub for Takuya Aoki for Urawa.
Nagoya awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 64, Yuki Muto (Urawa) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In Nagoya Nagoya attack through Gabriel Xavier. The finish is off target, however.
Ball goes out of play for a Urawa goal kick.
In the minute 69, Kosuke Ota is replacing Gabriel Xavier for the home team.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a Nagoya throw-in in Urawa's half.
Urawa's Ryosuke Yamanaka breaks free at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium. But the strike goes wide of the post.
In the minute 72, Goal kick for Nagoya at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium.
Free kick Nagoya.
Nagoya are pushing forward but Mateus's finish is wide of the goal.
In the minute 74, Masaaki Iemoto awards Urawa a goal kick.
Nagoya pushes forward through Mateus, whose finish on goal is saved.
Corner awarded to Nagoya.
In the minute 75, Nagoya have been awarded a corner by Masaaki Iemoto.
Yuichi Maruyama (Nagoya) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
Ball goes out of play for a Urawa goal kick.
In the minute 76, Leonardo keeps the away team in the match by reducing the deficit to 6-2.
Takahiro Sekine with an assist there.
Throw-in for Nagoya in the half of Urawa.
In the minute 79, Urawa have been awarded a corner by Masaaki Iemoto.
Urawa's Ryosuke Yamanaka breaks free at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium. But the strike goes wide of the post.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Nagoya.
In the minute 82, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Nagoya make their fourth substitution with Ryogo Yamasaki replacing Mu Kanazaki.
Massimo Ficcadenti is making the team's fifth substitution at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium with Ryotaro Ishida replacing Mateus.
In the minute 84, The away team replace Daiki Hashioka with Katsuya Iwatake.
Masaaki Iemoto signals a throw-in for Nagoya, close to Urawa's area.
Nagoya drives forward and Yuki Soma gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In the minute 86, Corner awarded to Nagoya.
Goal kick for Urawa at Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium.
Can Nagoya get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Urawa's half?
In the minute 87, Free kick for Urawa in their own half.
Nagoya drive upfield and Yosuke Akiyama gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Urawa defender.
Free kick in a good position for Nagoya!
In the minute 89, Nagoya drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Nagoya to take a throw-in in Urawa territory.
At Nagoya Mizuho Athletics Stadium the fourth official shows that 3 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
Nagoya awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Full-time! The final score is 6-2.
